00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,360
we have the initiation activity

3
00:02:09,480 --> 00:02:12,520
I’m sorry but I have to go to the office that day.

4
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:15,520
Behind me are the gear badges made for your year.

5
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:18,440
I want to be your boyfriend.

6
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:21,640
Can you take care of it for me?

7
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,840
But I have already had someone else’s gear in my care.

8
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:28,600
So where is…the reward you promise to give me?

9
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,680
That’s your reward.

10
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,400
Arthit,

11
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,200
I have an urgent task that needs your help

12
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:45,920
Can you check the price of transformer devices?

13
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:48,280
Please summarize them in a price list for me

14
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:49,240
Got it.

15
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,040
Let’s get going, Earth.

16
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:50,600
All set?

17
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,320
Yes.

18
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:58,760
Arthit,

19
00:02:58,960 --> 00:02:59,880
Yes?

20
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,400
I have an important matter that needs your favor

21
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:04,920
Well, we have a trouble with one supplier

22
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:07,240
They suddenly cancel their supplies for us.

23
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:10,200
I want you to find a new supplier

24
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:13,160
that can manufacture the plastic spoons like this for me.

25
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,560
I can do that

26
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:19,080
but I need to complete Khun Danai’s assignment first.

27
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:19,880
Arthit,

28
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,480
this is very urgent matter.

29
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:22,560
Right now,

30
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:23,800
the Production Department has made the blenders

31
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:26,240
that are supposed to have this kind of spoons as freebies

32
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:28,360
If we fail to get a new supplier

33
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:30,360
we are going to have trouble with the Production Department

34
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,320
Okay.

35
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,400
I leave it to you

36
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:44,720
Hello, Sawasdee krap.

37
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:46,280
Yes,

38
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:48,520
is this Muang Man Plastic company?

39
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:51,120
I’m calling from Ocean Electrics.

40
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,640
It’s too late, right?

41
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:12,760
Arthit,

42
00:04:13,040 --> 00:04:14,760
what are you doing?

43
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:17,000
I’m trying to find a manufacturer

44
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,880
that can make the plastic spoons like this.

45
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:21,120
Haven’t we ordered these spoons already?

46
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,040
Yes,

47
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:24,960
but P’John said the supplier we dealt

48
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:26,920
has just cancelled all of our orders.

49
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,720
Again?

50
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,840
Do you happen to know

51
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:33,600
who made the call and had these spoons made?

52
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:35,440
It’s Siam Polimer Group.

53
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,640
I think it should be Win

54
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:40,480
But we haven’t ordered from this company for quite some time

55
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,480
Get the contact number of Win

56
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:44,200
or the company number from Earth

57
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:45,520
Got it

58
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,520
Good luck.

59
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:52,880
What’s up, Arthit?

60
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:54,400
Aha?

61
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:57,720
Win?

62
00:04:58,440 --> 00:05:00,160
I’ll find you his number.

63
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:07,240
What’s the matter, Earth?

64
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:09,880
Arthit is asking for Win’s number

65
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:12,920
He wants to get Siam Polimer Group’s contact

66
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:15,400
to produce plastic spoons for the blenders we are making.

67
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,360
What?

68
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:19,840
I signed off last week to John to make the order.

69
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:22,240
Why do we need to find a new manufacturer?

70
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:26,520
Let me find the contact number for Arthit.

71
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,600
"Win"

72
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:37,680
Sales Department, Siam Polimer Group.

73
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:44,360
Are you going to the office now?

74
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,080
I’m not going back there today.

75
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:48,120
I have an errand to run for my family.

76
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:50,680
If you don’t have anything to clear you can go home as well

77
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,040
If you get back to the office from here,

78
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,560
it would be around the end of business day anyway.

79
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,160
Okay ka.

80
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,320
How is it going, Arthit?

81
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,200
Any update?

82
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:04,040
I still cannot reach them

83
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,560
Well then, let’s go to their company now

84
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:07,960
I go with you.

85
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:11,080
If we drive, we should catch them before they getting off from work

86
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,160
Okay.

87
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:13,240
Let’s go.

88
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,400
Sawasdee ka.

89
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,880
What are you guys doing?

90
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:22,240
Oh, we are searching for a company to apply our internships.

91
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,560
You just finish your class?

92
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:24,560
Yes.

93
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:26,720
Do you happen to see Day?

94
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,320
The teacher is asking for him.

95
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:33,400
Oh, that young man?

96
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:35,160
We are here for a while.

97
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,400
We haven’t seen them.

98
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,400
Is he causing any trouble?

99
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,360
Not at all, P’Tew

100
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,360
He has been absent for days.

101
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:45,440
Well, since we got back from the off-campus initiation

102
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,320
We should leave you guys now.

103
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,240
Sawasdee ka

104
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:04,520
P’Yong,

105
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:08,480
I wonder why we don’t order supplies from Siam Polimer?

106
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,440
I don’t know either.

107
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:11,640
But in the past,

108
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,720
we ordered from them very often.

109
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:14,920
It could be that Win has left our company

110
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,800
and no one keeps contact with Siam Polimer

111
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:19,080
What kind of person P’Win is?

112
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,680
Win is a very talented person.

113
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,480
He’s the top performer of the Procurement Department

114
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,640
Come to think of it,

115
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,920
he’s like you.

116
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:27,560
Starting at the Production

117
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:29,400
and got transferred to the Procurement.

118
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:31,320
Earth didn’t tell you anything?

119
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:32,720
No.

120
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,600
Why?

121
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:36,720
Well, Earth and Win…

122
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:40,960
Forget it.

123
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,840
We make a turn here and we are there

124
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:58,440
Wait a sec.

125
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:01,920
What’s up, Cherry?

126
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,320
P’Yong,

127
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:05,560
May I go in there first?

128
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,240
Sure, I’ll go there soon.

129
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:10,400
Look at the shelf.

130
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,600
Sawasdee krap.

131
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:13,760
What can I do for you?

132
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:16,400
I’m here to see the Sales Department.

133
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:18,160
Have you made an appointment?

134
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:20,760
No, I haven’t.

135
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:24,280
I think you better come here again tomorrow in the morning

136
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,440
Right now,

137
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:27,960
all of the employees have left the office

138
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:29,960
Well, I’m so sorry.

139
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:31,960
This is very urgent.

140
00:08:32,040 --> 00:08:36,360
Can you help check if there’s anyone can come and get my request?

141
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,400
I have to follow the rules here.

142
00:08:38,560 --> 00:08:41,200
The business hours here are over.

143
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:42,800
I’m really sorry

144
00:08:43,920 --> 00:08:45,160
Prayat.

145
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,600
Yes, sir?

146
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,920
What’s going on?

147
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:52,840
This young man said he wanted to meet someone in the Sales

148
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:56,080
I told him that we are closed for today

149
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,760
Let him in.

150
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:59,000
I can take his request.

151
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,600
Yes, sir.

152
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:01,760
This way, please.

153
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,800
Thank you so much.

154
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,920
The last minute order like this

155
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:10,360
has a very high cost of production than normal lead time.

156
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,560
Are you okay?

157
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:12,720
You haven’t come to class for many days.

158
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:14,000
This is my family matter.

159
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:14,800
I can handle it.

160
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,320
For this kind of problem,

161
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,160
you should not handle it alone.

162
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:20,560
You like to do things complicatedly

163
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:22,200
like the former guy who sat here

164
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,360
The owner of Bonus.

165
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:24,800
My name is Arthit

166
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,560
from Ocean Electrics.

167
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:28,080
What’s the urgent matter

168
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,840
you want the Sales Department here to help you with?

169
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:30,480
Well,

170
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:33,080
our company made an error in one of the supplies we had ordered

171
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,920
So I need to find a new supplier

172
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,120
that can manufacture this product with this specification

173
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,720
Look here, Khun Kerkkrai.

174
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:46,880
We need this product within this week.

175
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:49,960
I do understand that the short notice like this

176
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:52,880
means I may cut in the line of productions.

177
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:55,600
And interfere the production of your company.

178
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:57,720
Since I’m from the Procurement of my company

179
00:09:58,040 --> 00:09:59,640
this is the problem I have to solve

180
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:01,520
it’s my responsibility.

181
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:04,440
Please help consider this request, Khun Kerkkrai

182
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:08,560
You know, right?

183
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:10,120
The last minute order like this

184
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:12,680
has a very high cost of production than normal lead time

185
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,320
Yes, I know.

186
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:16,720
I will give you the best price I can.

187
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:19,600
But you don’t have the power to make such decision

188
00:10:20,280 --> 00:10:22,560
You can do what you just said, right?

189
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,200
I’ll do my best

190
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:25,360
Good.

191
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:28,000
I will authorize this line of production for you.

192
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:30,680
Thank you so much, Khun Kerkkrai.

193
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:36,040
Actually, my company has long been a supplier for your company.

194
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,840
But our contract was terminated.

195
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:40,520
In the past, there’s a guy from your company

196
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:43,160
come to our company every now and then.

197
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,720
Your name is Arthit, right?

198
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:48,080
Yes, sir.

199
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:52,680
Good, I haven’t seen a person who is as hardworking as you in a while

200
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:55,080
I help take care of this.

201
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:57,640
Thank you so much, Khun Kerkkrai.

202
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:03,200
Here’s for you.

203
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:04,200
Enough, M.

204
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:06,320
I normally don’t eat this much.

205
00:11:06,520 --> 00:11:08,000
You will get fat.

206
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:09,960
Many make juniors like to come to you.

207
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,400
Eat a lot and get fat.

208
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,720
What are you talking about?

209
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:14,080
What are you having in your mind?

210
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,960
By the way, where did you apply for your internship?

211
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:23,120
I and Pray just submitted our application to Unit All

212
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:25,240
It’s the food industrial company.

213
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,880
Really? We have the same mind.

214
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:29,760
Are you kidding?

215
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,280
Have you submitted your application?

216
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:34,840
The teacher said this company gave our university 2 spots

217
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:37,800
If you haven’t submitted it, you must hurry or it’ll be too late

218
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:44,080
Hey, that’s Tew, right?

219
00:11:47,520 --> 00:11:48,760
Focus on your study.

220
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,440
Don’t worry about your granny.

221
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:52,320
She’s under doctor’s care.

222
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:02,680
Day!

223
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:07,920
It’s a pity you didn’t go to the beach with us.

224
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:10,720
I was busy

225
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:13,760
Well, are you okay?

226
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,720
You haven’t come to class for many days.

227
00:12:16,040 --> 00:12:17,040
I’m okay

228
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:19,920
Please excuse me.

229
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:21,120
Hey, Day.

230
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:24,080
Is there anything that is troubling your mind?

231
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,800
No, there is not.

232
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,280
Another thing is,

233
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:29,600
this is my family matter.

234
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:32,200
I can handle it.

235
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:35,800
Hey, Day.

236
00:12:35,920 --> 00:12:38,760
I don’t know if you can handle it alone or not.

237
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:40,760
For this kind of problem,

238
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:43,320
you should not handle it alone

239
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,320
Hey,

240
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:49,120
why do you like to butt in my personal life?

241
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:52,720
Let me make it clear right here.

242
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,880
Stop messing with me

243
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,440
I want to be alone.

244
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:02,680
Hey.

245
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:04,520
M, don’t.

246
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:05,560
Don’t.

247
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,080
Why?

248
00:13:07,160 --> 00:13:08,720
Leave them alone.

249
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,800
Mom.

250
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:16,680
I have to answer this call of my mother.

251
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:57,440
you are still here, Arthit?

252
00:13:57,720 --> 00:14:00,440
Well, I just got back from the factory.

253
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:03,600
and I just completed with the plastic spoons case.

254
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:07,160
What about you, P’Earth?

255
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:10,160
Ah,

256
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:12,400
I come back here to get some document

257
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:17,240
I saw that the water in Bonus’ bowl is dirty so I changed.

258
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:19,640
I’m about to leave, though.

259
00:14:19,760 --> 00:14:21,080
Do you want to come with me?

260
00:14:21,560 --> 00:14:22,800
Nah,

261
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:26,360
I still haven’t done the transformer price list that Khun Danai assigned to me

262
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,760
You can go without me.

263
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,480
It’s okay

264
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:31,160
Let me help. It will be done faster

265
00:14:31,520 --> 00:14:33,280
We can go home together

266
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:35,040
It’s pretty late

267
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:37,680
Yes.

268
00:14:41,680 --> 00:14:43,200
How far have you done?

269
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,240
Well…

270
00:14:48,920 --> 00:14:51,560
If I know the date, I’ll call and let you know again.

271
00:14:52,640 --> 00:14:54,040
I have to go.

272
00:14:58,560 --> 00:14:59,800
Lady first.

273
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:03,880
Hey, Kong.

274
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:05,000
I will walk May home first.

275
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:06,160
Are you sure you are okay?

276
00:15:06,400 --> 00:15:07,200
I am.

277
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:08,320
Are you going now?

278
00:15:08,520 --> 00:15:09,880
Yes.

